---
title: divide_polynomialcoeff (fulu-polynomial-commitments-sampling)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_copy : a = copy(a)
    q_copy --> q_init_vars : o = [], apos = len(a) - 1, bpos = len(b) - 1
    q_init_vars --> q_check_diff : diff = apos - bpos
    q_check_diff --> q_quot : diff >= 0
    q_check_diff --> q_return : diff < 0
    q_quot --> q_compute : quot = a[apos] / b[bpos]
    q_compute --> q_prepend : o.insert(0, quot)
    q_prepend --> q_subtract : a[diff + i] -= b[i] * quot
    q_subtract --> q_decrement : apos -= 1, diff -= 1
    q_decrement --> q_check_diff : diff = apos - bpos
    q_return --> [*] : return o

    note right of q_check_diff
        INV: b must not be the zero polynomial
        INV: a = quotient * b + remainder (remainder is discarded)
        INV: Leading coefficient of b (b[bpos]) must be nonzero
    end note
